===============================
BLOCK COMMANDS (Place a block and grab it while saying :h)
===============================
- Grab blocks using player chat commands
    :block - switch current level to staff only (on/off)
    :db - removes the block
    :dmb - destroys all of your blocks in the vicinity
    :fl <level> - sends '/find <level>' command to RC
    :ga <gani> - sets block to the specified gani
    :gs - a list of grabbed-by stats on this block
    :h - pm's you a list of these commands
    :i <image> - updates your block to specified image
    :image - sends you the block's image name
    :l - sends level name to 'Other' tab in RC
    :moo - disco light effect on block
    :msg <player> - send a PM to the specified player
    :sendtonc - send an echo/message to NC
    :so - makes block only visible to staff
    :tp - the time this block was placed

===============================
RC COMMANDS
===============================
- /find *era_hat-* (Broad search, will pull up every files with this pattern)
- /scriptscan scripts Test (Will search every NPCs, Classes and Weapons all at once for the keyword you use replaced by Test)
To narrow your search, replace scripts with NPC, WEAPON, or CLASS in the command.


===============================
Chat Commands (:)  what they do
===============================

------------------------------------
Warp / Summon / Reconnect / Unstick
------------------------------------
:s <acc>  Summon player to you. Lots of checks (bounty/nosummon/quest rooms).

:w <acc>  Warp to player (respects warp privacy + quest protections).

:rp <acc>  Reconnect a player. Staff-gated.

:u <acc|level> [where]  Unstick target (or everyone in level if level).
------------------------------------
Movement / Speed / PK / God
------------------------------------
:tpk [acc]  Toggle PK (staff invis SP). Shows PK Toggle: on/off.

:tf [acc]  Toggle fast movement. Shows Speed Toggle: on/off.

:wh  Play warp home ani (visual warp-in).

(Hidden) godMode2 exists server-side; client hotkey path is effectively disabled.
------------------------------------
Items / Inventory / Currency
------------------------------------
:ai(*) <id> <amt>  Add item (spawn). Staff-right checked + ID validation + logs.

:ri(*) <id> <amt|all>  Remove item (or all of that ID). Logs.

:da  Drop ALL items onto ground (except protected ones). Super-admin only.

:sc <acc> <amt>  Give Staff Coin(s) (item 949) with limits. Logs.

:discordaward <acc> <amt>  Give Discord Coin(s) (item 1904), usually max 1. Logs.

:fi <name>  Find item by name (lists IDs).

:ii <id>  Item info (id, name, image, weapon).

:vi <account> View players inventory.

:invmanager(*) Inventory manager for admins, used to spawn.
------------------------------------
Cars / Levels / Warps
------------------------------------
:car(*) <id> <acc?>  Spawn car at you (rights-gated). Logs.

:tow  Tow clicked car (via mouse).

:cl  Check level (scan file for updates/spawners). Logs.

:sa  Set auction house location (toggles AuctionWarper).

:open / :close <reason>  Open/Close clicked warp; closing kicks non-staff out + sets reason.

:il  Add current level to ignore list (client-side).
------------------------------------
Guild / Hats / Animation
------------------------------------
:g <guild>  Set guild (supports level mass apply, clr to clear). Rights-gated + logs.

:seth <acc> <hatimg|id>  Set hat on target. Logs.

:ga <gani> <acc|all|level>  Set animation (respects restrictions + logs).

------------------------------------
Buffs
------------------------------------

:tbuff <acc>  Temp buff (~30s strength; freeze/ani poke; RC notice if < L4).

:buff <acc>  Full buff (~5 hours): strength/worker/vitality/lightweight + heal.

:tintin [acc]  +1 week Infinite Ammo (adds time to unlimitedAmmo). Logs.
------------------------------------
Bank / Trading
------------------------------------
:cb <acc>  Check bank balance (L4 only). Logs.

:tradelock <acc>  Toggle trade lock on player; RC + logs.
------------------------------------
Favorites / Warps
------------------------------------
:wt <#>  Warp to stored location (slot 115).

:st <#> <label>  Store location (currently disabled in code via early break).

:hs  Intended Hide Favorites, but sends a server op without a handler (no-op). Use GUI auto-hide instead.

:sf Pulls up the list of your 10 favorite levels.
------------------------------------
NPC Utilities (mouse-based)
------------------------------------
:np <class>  Place NPC of class at mouse (spawns a putClass).

:bl  Place level blocker at mouse (removable with :de by L4).

:nd  NPC data on clicked NPC (classes/img/dir/pos/owners). Client printout.

:ns <dbnpc>  Summon DB-NPC to you.

:nw <dbnpc>  Warp to DB-NPC.
------------------------------------
Misc
------------------------------------
:r  Reconnect to server (serverwarp to current).

:ks  Toggle kill sound (stops midi if active).

:sl <class>  Scan level for NPCs of class (shows closest + details; cleans old item 2015).

:file <pattern>  Find file(s) and list names.

:help  Shows a HelpBox (restricted to a specific account).
=========================================================
(*) = requires higher staff (often L4/admin) or a specific right. Exact gating varies per action.
=========================================================

